{"tid":2515352,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"立法會委員會提出港台珍貴節目商品化","createTime":"2021-05-04T02:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T02:46:30.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b9a018a73ae7b64ba9fb3d7391947edb33545e2f","tid":2515352,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:28:44.000Z","msg":"難怪YouTube 節目要下架。<br />\n<br />\n今年3月立法會會議，委員會已經有人提出將港台珍貴節目商品化，包括將節目出售。反映了委員會未有視港台節目為公共資產，並將這些資料企圖私有化，更差情況可能如收費OTT服務一樣，需要登記及繳費才能觀賞節目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma7PJXGY9E7i9msCzCiRpZyBV13hC8XXaXHS7ZbAMSi9z?filename=1XwKZxj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1XwKZxj.png&h=4caec0f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr20-21/chinese/panels/itb/papers/itb20210315cb1-652-5-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr20-21%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Fitb%2Fpapers%2Fitb20210315cb1-652-5-c.pdf&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=1d4484db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr20-21/chinese/panels/itb/papers/itb20210315cb1-652-5-c.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"c3b459509f072ef07536fcb32f30d0b84c2be46b","tid":2515352,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:46:30.000Z","msg":"push"}]}